men's 400 metres hurdles|56.58 \n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{iaaf name|id=135236|name=Fani Halkia}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{succession box|before={{flagicon|RUS}} [[Yuliya Pechonkina]]|title=[[400 metres hurdles#Women's Seasons Best|Women's 400 m Hurdles Best Year Performance]]|years=2004|after={{flagicon|RUS}} [[Yuliya Pechonkina]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Footer Olympic Champions 400 m hurdles Women}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Chalkia, Fani}}\n[[Category:1979 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Greek female hurdlers]]\n[[Category:Greek female sprinters]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Larissa]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic athletes of Greece]]\n[[Category:Olympic gold medalists for Greece]]\n[[Category:Doping cases in athletics]]\n[[Category:Greek sportspeople in doping cases]]\n[[Category:European Athletics Championships medalists]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympiacos Athletics athletes]]\n[[Category:Olympic gold medalists in athletics (track and field)]]\n\n\n{{Greece-Olympic-medalist-stub}}\n{{greece-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox sportsperson\n| image = \n| caption = \n| native_name = \u03a6\u03b1\u03bd\u03ae \u03a7\u03b1\u03bb\u03ba\u03b9\u03ac\n| native_name_lang = \n| birth_date = {{nowrap|{{birth date and age|df=yes|1979|02|02}}}}\n| birth_place = [[Larissa, Greece|Larissa]], Greece\n| height =\n| weight =\n| country = {{GRE}}\n| sport = Athletics\n| event = [[400 metres hurdles]]\n| coach =\n| highestranking = 1st\n| pb = 52.77 sec\n| medaltemplates =\n{{Medal|Competition|[[Olympic Games]]}}\n{{Medal|Gold|[[2004 Summer Olympics|2004 Athens]]|[[Athletics at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 400 metres hurdles|400 m hurdles]]}}\n{{Medal|Competition | [[European Athletics Championships|European Championships]]}}\n{{Medal|Silver|[[2006 European Athletics Championships|2006 Got